---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Pool Builders Burleigh Heads | Hill, Beachside, Renovation | (03) 9003 0108"
  description="Swimming pool builders and resurfacing for Burleigh Heads — Burleigh Hill modernist new builds, 1980s beachside pool resurface, character-zone integration. Glass fence + ocean salt specialists.">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://goldcoastpoolbuilders.com.au/burleigh-heads/">
  </Fragment>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Burleigh Heads &middot; Burleigh Hill &middot; West Burleigh</span>
      <h1>Pool builders &amp; resurfacers in <span class="accent">Burleigh Heads</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Burleigh is two pool markets in one suburb. Beachside (between James Street
        and the ocean) is original 1970s&ndash;90s pool stock now overdue for
        resurfacing. Burleigh Hill and the West Burleigh modernist new-build wave is
        all premium freeform concrete with full-tile interior and infinity-edge over
        the headland or the creek.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book a free on-site quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Why Burleigh Heads</span>
      <h2>The Burleigh Heads pool story.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Burleigh Hill = freeform concrete with a view.</h3>
        <p>
          Burleigh Hill rebuilds (2010s onwards) are some of the highest-spec residential
          pool projects on the entire Gold Coast. Architect-designed houses on
          north-east-facing slope blocks looking out over Tallebudgera Creek or the
          headland. Pools are <strong>freeform concrete with full mosaic-tile
          interior, dark glass-mosaic accent walls, fully-frameless glass fencing
          for unobstructed view</strong>, and increasingly an infinity edge or
          knife-edge weir to extend the visual line into the landscape. Budgets
          run $150K&ndash;$400K for the pool alone before deck, surround and
          cabana.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Beachside Burleigh = resurface territory.</h3>
        <p>
          The original Burleigh beachside grid (between Goodwin Terrace, Park Avenue
          and the Gold Coast Highway) was developed 1960s&ndash;80s. Pools added
          1975&ndash;1995 are now <strong>30&ndash;50 years old</strong>. Most
          have been resurfaced once already; many are due for a second pebble&rarr;quartz
          refit OR a full structural assessment to decide resurface-vs-rebuild. We
          do that assessment honestly &mdash; if the rebar is going, we&rsquo;ll
          tell you. If it&rsquo;s sound, you save $60K by resurfacing instead of
          rebuilding.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Character / heritage overlay considerations.</h3>
        <p>
          Parts of Burleigh Heads sit in a <strong>Burleigh Hill Local Character
          Area</strong> and small parts touch a Heritage Overlay (older queenslander
          stock along James Street area). Pools themselves are exempt from heritage
          assessment, but the <strong>surrounding paving, fencing, and any pool
          cabana</strong> need to match the character &mdash; no harsh-edge modernist
          surrounds on a pre-1950 cottage. City of Gold Coast planning officer will
          flag this at certification if missed. We design with the existing
          architectural language in mind.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Typical Burleigh Heads jobs.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Burleigh Hill freeform concrete with infinity edge + mosaic-tile interior ($180K&ndash;$320K)</li>
          <li>1980s beachside pool resurface to Quartzon + new travertine coping ($18K&ndash;$26K)</li>
          <li>West Burleigh creek-side concrete with creek-view glass fence ($90K&ndash;$140K)</li>
          <li>Burleigh-character cottage backyard fibreglass install with timber decking surround ($55K&ndash;$80K)</li>
          <li>Pre-sale pool safety remediation (Form 23 compliance work) for older Burleigh stock</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Other service areas.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/mermaid-beach/">Mermaid Beach</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/mudgeeraba/">Mudgeeraba</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/robina/">Robina</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/helensvale/">Helensvale</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/city-of-gold-coast/">All City of Gold Coast</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free Burleigh Heads on-site quote.</h2>
        <p>Hill, beachside or West Burleigh creek-side. Architectural design coordination. Honest resurface vs rebuild call.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
